The '''Capitol''',<ref name="Shuttle DB">{{Databank|orn-free-taa-s-shuttle|Orn Free Taa's Shuttle}}</ref> or '''capitol building''', was the main government building in [[Lessu City]], the [[capital]] [[city]] of [[Ryloth]]. Located in the [[Octagon district]], it was the headquarters for the [[Ryloth Head Clan]].<ref name="Dawn">''[[Star Wars: Dawn of Rebellion: The Visual Guide]]''</ref> When the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems|Separatists]] [[Battle of Ryloth|occupied]] Ryloth during the [[Clone Wars]], [[Emir of Ryloth|Emir]] [[Wat Tambor]] used the building as his headquarters.<ref name="Liberty on Ryloth" />

Later, after the [[Proclamation of the New Order|formation]] of the [[Galactic Empire]], the building became the Empire's [[planet]]ary headquarters. Opening on a large plaza where speeches from planetary leaders took place,<ref name="Devil's Deal" /> the Capitol also contained offices, detention cells, and a private [[hangar]] where [[Senator]] [[Orn Free Taa]] kept his [[Orn Free Taa's shuttle|personal shuttle]].<ref name="Rescue on Ryloth" />

